    <h4>Why is it important to have good, functioning wipers?</h4>
    <p>
        Bad wiper blades are the 3rd biggest mechanical reason for car accidents.  23% of all car crashes in the U.S. are weather related.
    </p>
    <h4>Do you ship wiper blades or just the inserts?</h4>
