    </p>
    <h4>What is the difference between wiper blades and wiper inserts?</h4>
    <p>
        Wiper inserts are the rubber portion of the wiper blade.  Replacing the insert can be a frustrating task whose grief simply isn't worth the money savings.  
        That is why we only ship the full wiper blade assembly so that replacing your wiper blades is quick and easy.
    </p>
